1188 private SoapArrayInfo ParseArrayType(string value)
1189 {
1190 if (value == null)
1191 {
1192 throw new ArgumentNullException(System.SR.Format(System.SR.XmlMissingArrayType, CurrentTag()));
1193 }
1194 if (value.Length == 0)
1195 {
1196 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Format(System.SR.XmlEmptyArrayType, CurrentTag()), "value");
1197 }
1198 char[] array = value.ToCharArray();
1199 int num = array.Length;
1200 SoapArrayInfo result = default(SoapArrayInfo);
1201 int num2 = num - 1;
1202 if (array[num2] != ']')
1203 {
1204 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.XmlInvalidArraySyntax, "value");
1205 }
1206 num2--;
1207 while (num2 != -1 && array[num2] != '[')
1208 {
1209 if (array[num2] == ',')
1210 {
1211 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Format(System.SR.XmlInvalidArrayDimentions, CurrentTag()), "value");
1212 }
1213 num2--;
1214 }
1215 if (num2 == -1)
1216 {
1217 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.XmlMismatchedArrayBrackets, "value");
1218 }
1219 int num3 = num - num2 - 2;
1220 if (num3 > 0)
1221 {
1222 string text = new string(array, num2 + 1, num3);
1223 try
1224 {
1225 result.length = int.Parse(text, CultureInfo.InvariantCulture);
1226 }
1227 catch (Exception ex)
1228 {
1229 if (ex is OutOfMemoryException)
1230 {
1231 throw;
1232 }
1233 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Format(System.SR.XmlInvalidArrayLength, text), "value");
1234 }
1235 }
1236 else
1237 {
1238 result.length = -1;
1239 }
1240 num2--;
1241 result.jaggedDimensions = 0;
1242 while (num2 != -1 && array[num2] == ']')
1243 {
1244 num2--;
1245 if (num2 < 0)
1246 {
1247 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.XmlMismatchedArrayBrackets, "value");
1248 }
1249 if (array[num2] == ',')
1250 {
1251 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Format(System.SR.XmlInvalidArrayDimentions, CurrentTag()), "value");
1252 }
1253 if (array[num2] != '[')
1254 {
1255 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.XmlInvalidArraySyntax, "value");
1256 }
1257 num2--;
1258 result.jaggedDimensions++;
1259 }
1260 result.dimensions = 1;
1261 result.qname = new string(array, 0, num2 + 1);
1262 return result;
1263 }
